data.name: label84.Text
data.value:
Fixtures needs to be adjusted if you've added a team onto a new career mode competition. If you've added London Irish for example to Super Rugby, replacing Jaquares, replace all the Jaquares fixtures with their team ID.
You can assign the value 0 to Unkown ID to make the fixture not work anymore. Caution should be exercised when looking at the Round ID and Unkown ID values.

data.name: label82.Text
data.value: Only change this if you are adding or moving teams in career mode. This should be equal to the competition ID you're adding the team. If you adding a new team, remember to blank the old team's value.
